6. **Return buffer**: `return writer.buffer();` - Returns the complete serialized data as a `std::vector<uint8_t>`

The serialized format will be: `[header (2 bytes)][data length prefix][data bytes][16 bytes of 0x00 padding][footer (4 bytes)]`

